title: The Who's best albums
description:
One of the greatest rock bands ever, this torrent gives you their five most important studio albums: Tommy, (1969), Who's Next, (1971), Quadrophenia, (1973), The Who by Numbers, (1975), & Who Are You, (1978.)  It's also got 2 live albums, including the legendary Live at Leeds, (1970), and Live at the Isle of Wight Festival 1970, (released in 1996,)  along with My Generation: The Very Best of the Who, (1996), so that you'll have all their early hits.
